<div i18n:domain="schooltool">
  <p i18n:translate="">
    SchoolTool is free administrative software for schools around the
    world.  The goals of the project are to create a simple turnkey
    student information system or managment information system for
    primary and secondary schools, as well as a framework for building
    customized applications and configurations for individual schools
    or states.
  </p>
  <p i18n:translate="">
    SchoolTool is built on a 100% open source software stack, written
    in <a href="http://python.org" i18n:name="python"
    i18n:translate="">Python</a> using the <a href="http://zope.org"
    i18n:name="zope3" i18n:translate="">Zope 3</a> framework.
  </p>
  <p i18n:translate="">
    SchoolTool is licensed under the <a
    href="http://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl-2.0.html" i18n:name="gpl"
    i18n:translate="">GNU General Public License, Version 2</a>.
  </p>
